    "find_text": "v - ?",
    "solution": "1. Acceleration is a = g * sin(α).\n2. sin(α) = opposite side / hypotenuse = h / L = 6/10 = 0.6.\n3. a = 10 * 0.6 = 6 m/s^2.\n4. Speed at the end from v^2 = v0^2 + 2*a*L: v = sqrt(2*a*L).\n5. v = sqrt(2 * 6 * 10) = sqrt(120) ≈ 10.95 m/s.",
