    "title": "What minimum force must be applied along an inclined plane with angle 30° to hold a body of mass 2 kg? Friction is absent.",
    "problem_text": "What minimum force must be applied along an inclined plane with angle 30° to hold a body of mass 2 kg? Friction is absent.",
